extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value:
Each Yu-Gi-Oh! TCG Speed Duel: Twisted Nightmares Starter Deck contains:
• 1 x 30-Card Bakura Deck
• 1 x 30-Card Marik Deck
• 4 Skill Cards (2 for Bakura and 2 for Marik)
• 2 Ultra Rare variant cards
